            <title><![CDATA[GTA 6 Trailer Passes 100 Million Views On YouTube In Less Than A Week]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/gta-6-trailer-passes-100-million-views-on-youtube-in-less-than-a-week/1100-6531463/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
