    </p><p>Sorry, but you can't access this content!</p></div>
          <p><em>Now Playing:</em> GTA 6 (Grand Theft Auto VI) - Official Release Date Reveal | Trailer 2</p>
      </div>
<p dir="ltr">Days before the trailer dropped, Rockstar revealed that <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/gta-6-delayed-to-2026/1100-6531282/">Grand Theft Auto VI would be delayed to May 26, 2026</a>. Previously, the game was set to arrive this fall. However, there was always skepticism about that release window because <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/gta-6-is-scheduled-for-2025-but-rockstar-has-a-history-of-delays/1100-6519700/">Rockstar has a lengthy history of delays</a>.</p><p dir="ltr">Grand Theft Auto VI is one of the most anticipated video games ever. One research company believes the Rockstar title <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/gta-5-could-make-3-billion-in-first-year-alone/1100-6528605/">could sell 40 million copies and make $3 billion dollars</a> after just a year. Meanwhile, Circana believed <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/gta-6-and-switch-2-will-help-video-game-industry-rebound-in-2025-analyst-predicts/1100-6526016/">Grand Theft Auto VI would help the overall gaming industry bounce back</a> this year, along with Switch 2's launch, before the game was pushed back to 2026.</p><p dir="ltr">So far, Grand Theft Auto VI is only confirmed for PS5 and Xbox Series X|S, though <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/gta-6-exec-talks-approach-to-pc-releases-but-doesnt-confirm-anything/1100-6529346/">a PC version is expected later down the road</a>. Meanwhile, Digital Foundry <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/gta-6-trailer-2-was-only-30fps-and-it-may-be-too-much-for-switch-2/1100-6531393/">doesn't believe the game will come to Switch 2</a> and even speculates it may not run on Steam Deck.</p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
